0bb814d10a287949de64484a3a5c6016e4878ce6.query:
insert into npc_replies (pattern, template, channel, to_mention, enabled, created_by) values
            ("^!twitter$", $3, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!youtube$", $4, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!clips$", $5, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!vod(?:s)?(?:-)?(?:channel)?(?:s)?$", $6, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!reddit$", "reddit.com/r/PedroPeepos", $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!discord$", $7, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!instagram$", $8, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!tiktok$", $9, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!social(?:s)?$", $10, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("(?:^!stream$|\s*stream(?:ing)?\s+(?:today|now)\s*\?.*)$", "YEP Caedrel should be streaming today. Follow twitter.com/caedrelupdates for more updates", $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("(?:^!cast$|\s*cast(?:ing)?\s+(?:lec\s+)?today(?:\?)?|\s*lec\s+(?:on\+s)?today(?:\?)?|\s*lec\s+on(?:\?)?)", "Caedrel will cast FNC vs AST on Saturday (8th April), and KOI vs G2 on Sunday (9th April). You can find LEC schedule here lolesports.com/schedule?leagues=lec", $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!end(?:ing)?(?:-)?song$", "okaywill - Chicken Dinner: youtube.com/watch?v=B_rAI7zaVZU", $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!(?:nord)?(?:-)?vpn$", "Get NordVPN here nordvpn.com/caedrel, 30-day money-back guarantee with coupon code 'Caedrel' upon checkout", $2, 0, 1, $1),

            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:caedALLO|peepoSitHey|good\s+morning)(:?\s+)?.*", "caedALLO caedH", $2, 1, 0, $1),
            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:thanks|thank\s+you|thnx|ty)(?:\s+)?.*$", "ok", $2, 1, 0, $1),
            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:GIGACHAD|best\s+mod|good\s+mod|PETTHEMODS|<3|heart)(?:\s+)?.*", "caedH", $2, 1, 0, $1),
            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:bye)(?:\s+)?.*", "bye", $2, 1, 0, $1),
            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:Pog|PogU|POGGIES|POGGERS|caedPog)(?:\s+)?.*", "xddFlush", $2, 1, 0, $1),
            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:xdd.*)(?:\s+)?.*", "widexddL", $2, 1, 0, $1),
            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:Aware|TrollAware|TrollDespair|Despairge|xddDespair)(?:\s+)?.*", "Aware Despairge", $2, 1, 0, $1),
            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:DonoWall)(?:\s+)?.*", "classic DonoWall Despair", $2, 1, 0, $1);

2bb900daacc1c9a1594fcc8516a0a5ab0345f609.query:
select
                    name as "name!",
                    caster as "caster!",
                    date_of_birth as "date_of_birth: NaiveDate",
                    timezone,
                    seven_tv_id,
                    created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                    updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
                from channels
                where name = $1

b25ce0464a18f3685e62f37d6c97399934f06987.query:
select
                    id,
                    pattern,
                    case_insensitive,
                    template,
                    to_mention,
                    channel,
                    enabled,
                    created_by,
                    created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                    updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
                from npc_replies
                where enabled = 1 and (channel is null or channel = $1)
                order by id asc
